      • expandNodes

        public void expandNodes(java.util.List<DAGNode> nodesToExpand)
        Expands each node at a given depth of the graph in a separate thread. Making use of ExecutorService to manage thread reuse. Uses CountDownLatch to block the program continuing until all nodes for a given level have been expanded.
